00:03:10.700 --> 00:03:11.400
-

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:15.400
And our teachers, as every year, are going not to betray your trust. Applause!

00:03:22.100 --> 00:03:22.800
-

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:26.800
I congratulate our kind, clever, wise and responsive teachers. They love you very much and they are waiting for you.

00:03:31.100 --> 00:03:33.200
-

00:03:33.200 --> 00:03:37.200
They promise to love you, respect you and, of course, teach you.

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:42.000
-

