Let's open the very first page. Did everybody open it?

00:04:17.900 --> 00:04:19.100
-

00:04:19.100 --> 00:04:23.100
You came today for the first time to school, I believe, you'll manage everything, am I right, Nina?

00:04:30.300 --> 00:04:31.800
-

00:04:31.800 --> 00:04:35.800
You will study well, endeavor, and behave well. And what is important, kids, we will not only learn to read, count, write beautifully but also we will learn to be friends.

00:04:44.800 --> 00:04:45.100
-

00:04:45.100 --> 00:04:49.100
We are going to be a very friendly grade, no one is to offend anyone.

